The Vanguard fund offers investors a front-row seat to the agentic and physical AI revolution through a single, low-cost investment vehicle. The fund's large-cap focus provides stability while pursuing growth in emerging AI technologies, and its diversified approach and focus on established technology leaders help manage risk.
